            <div class="c-article-body">
                <div class="c-article-section__content c-article-section__content--standfirst" itemprop="description" lang="en"><p>If we are to learn how to develop a healthy society, we must transform history into an analytical, predictive science, argues Peter Turchin. He has identified intriguing patterns across vastly different times and places.</p></div>
                <noscript>
                    
                </noscript>
                
                    <div class="c-pdf-button__container">
                        
                            
    
